{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectProtocol"]]},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"title":"onNotify(flags:handler:)","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GLibObject","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ObjectRef"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolPAAE8onNotify5flags7handlerSiAA12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0B3RefV_AA09ParamSpecJ0VtctF"},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectProtocol\/onNotify(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onNotify","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ConnectFlags","text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ObjectRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpecRef"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}]}],"name":"flags"},{"name":"unownedSelf","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Reference to instance of self","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpec","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" of the property which changed."}]}],"name":"pspec"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"handler"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then any call to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"explicitNotify"},{"type":"text","text":", then this signal is emitted only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"when they explicitly call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"C","type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#canonical-parameter-names","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This represents the underlying ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/objectprotocol\/onnotify(flags:handler:)"]}],"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/ParamSpecRef":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/paramspecref","abstract":[{"code":"GParamSpec","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" encapsulates the metadata required to specify parameters, such as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpecRef","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ParamSpecRef"}],"title":"ParamSpecRef","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/ObjectRef":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"ObjectRef","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/objectref","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The base object type."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectRef","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/ObjectProtocol":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","navig